## UDisc identity

**Requires:** Player role (any user can set their own)

```
/set-udisc-name [username] [name]
```

Links your UDisc identity for automatic scorecard matching. At least one field is required.

| Option | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `username` | Your UDisc `@username` (e.g. `@janedoe`) |
| `name` | Your name as shown on UDisc scorecards |

This can also be set during [signup](/docs/getting-started#the-signup-form) and updated any time.

